&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step into the innovative world of LG Electronics. As a global leader in technology, LG Electronics is dedicated to creating innovative solutions for a better life. Our brand promise, &#39;Life&#39;s Good&#39;, embodies our commitment to ensuring a happier life for all. We have a rich history spanning over six decades and a global presence in over 290 locations.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Our diverse portfolio includes Home Appliance Solutions, Media Entertainment Solutions, Vehicle Solutions, and Eco Solutions. &amp;nbsp;Our management philosophy, &quot;Jeong-do Management,&quot; embodies our commitment to high ethical standards and transparent operations. Grounded in the principles of &#39;Customer-Value Creation&#39; and &#39;People-Oriented Management&#39;, these values shape our corporate culture, fostering creativity, diversity, and integrity. At LG, we believe in the power of collective wisdom through an inclusive work environment.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Join us and become a part of a company that is shaping the future of technology.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;At LG, we strive to make Life Good for Everyone.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ready to Power Up Your Summer? ⚡&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Spend your summer at LG Electronics, where innovation meets imagination!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Summer Internship Program isn’t just about gaining experience — it’s about building real skills, tackling real projects, and seeing your ideas come to life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At LG, you won’t be grabbing coffee (unless it’s for yourself 😉).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll collaborate with passionate teams, work on cutting-edge technology, and contribute to projects that impact millions of people around the world. From smart devices to sustainable solutions, you’ll get a front-row seat to how big ideas turn into real-world breakthroughs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Expect hands-on learning, mentorship from industry experts, networking opportunities, and a chance to explore what a future with a global tech leader could look like. Plus, you’ll connect with other ambitious students who are just as excited about innovation as you are.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re curious, driven, and ready to challenge yourself, this is your moment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let’s make this summer unforgettable — with LG. 🚀&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are actively seeking an undergraduate 2026 LG Summer Intern to join our &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Environmental Health &amp;amp; Safety Team.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;EHS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Internship&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is a 9-week program from &lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;June 1st&amp;nbsp; through July 31st&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The internship will be based in the office (Mon-Fri 8AM-5PM) at the &lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;LG North America Innovation Campus (HQ) in Englewood Cliffs, NJ&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; and pay an hourly rate of &lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;$25.00&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The LG Internship Program is built on the philosophy of ensuring that each intern is given the opportunity to perform robust and meaningful work while gaining real-world experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The program will also include each intern working on an individual strategic project for the department and delivering a presentation at the program’s end.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The main project for the &lt;strong&gt;EHS&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Intern is:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Support the development of AI-driven tools and prototypes designed to improve internal productivity, knowledge accessibility, and business process automation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Assisting in the development of internal generative AI applications, building automation workflows using AI models, and evaluating machine learning solutions that can support business operations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Contribute to the exploration and development of AI capabilities that can be integrated into future products, internal tools and workflows.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Gain hands on experience with cutting edge AI technologies while delivering meaningful insights and prototypes to support LG&#39;s AI strategy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To support the DXP AI Team in developing, testing and deploying AI-driven solutions that improve operational efficiency and enable data-driven decision making across the enterprise&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with engineers, product managers, and business stakeholders to assist in the development of machine learning and generative AI applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the development and testing of AI models, including large language model (LLM) based applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support data preparation, cleaning and feature engineering for machine learning workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct research on emerging AI technologies and identifying potential use cases relevant to business needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Qualifications&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Enrollment in a Bachelor&#39;s degree program at an accredited College/University.&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Rising Sophomore, Rising Junior in a business, data, or analytics related major is preferred&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Programing experience with Python preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior exposure to LLMs or generative AI technologies preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with GiT or version control systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of APIs and basic software development practices&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic skills in quantitative data analysis and be proficient in using Excel for creating charts and infographics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in tools such as Microsoft Office, Google,&amp;nbsp; Teams, and AI-based drawing tools is required for visualizing ideas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates a strong interest in diverse generations and cultures, particularly related to food lifestyles in both the U.S. and Korea&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curiosity and enthusiasm for customer observation, the ability to extract meaningful insights, and strong communication skills are essential qualities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mindset grounded in design thinking and the ability to approach and solve problems creatively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills, outgoing personality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Recruiting Range&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$25&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$25 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits Offered Full-Time Employees:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No-cost employee premiums for you and your eligible dependents for competitive medical, dental, vision and prescription benefits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Auto enrollment with immediate vesting of competitive company matching contributions in a 401(k) Retirement Savings Plan with several investment&amp;nbsp;options.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generous Paid Time Off program that includes company holidays and a combined bank of paid sick and vacation time. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performance based Short-Term Incentives (varies by role).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to confidential mental health resources to help you and your loved ones improve your quality of life. Personal fitness goal incentives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Family orientated benefits such as paid parental leave and support for families raising children with learning, social, behavioral challenges, or developmental disabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Group Rate Life and Disability Insurance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits Offered Temporary/Contractors: &amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Eligible for the relevant benefit programs offered through our partner agencies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://lge-careers.com/wp-content/themes/lg-career/assets/privacy-notice.pdf&quot;&gt;Privacy Notice to California Applicants&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants who need assistance or a reasonable accommodation during the hiring process may contact our team by phone at: 973-477-7090 or&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:support@lg4me.freshdesk.com&quot;&gt;support@lg4me.freshdesk.com. &lt;/a&gt;This email and phone number will only reply to accommodation requests and is not intended for general employment inquiries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At LG, we aspire to empower people and celebrate differences because we believe diversity will create the unexpected. We provide equal employment opportunity to all individuals regardless of their race, color, creed, religion, gender, age, sexual orientation, national origin, disability, veteran status, or any other characteristic protected by state, federal, or local law. Consistent with our commitment to providing equal opportunity and embracing diversity, LG has implemented affirmative action to ensure applicants are employed and employees are treated without regard to these characteristics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In addition to the above, LG believes that pay transparency is a key part of diversity, equity, and inclusion. Our salary ranges take into account many factors in making compensation decisions including but not limited to skillset, experience, licensure, certifications, internal equity, and other business needs. While we consider geographic pay differentials in final offers, because we operate in many geographies where applicable, the salary range listed may not reflect all geographic differentials applied&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
